TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: DECODE(TRUE, JO_CATG_CD = 'CA' OR JO_CATG_CD = 'CM' OR JO_CATG_CD = 'CV' OR JO_CATG_CD = 'PU' OR JO_CATG_CD = 'PV', 1, JO_CATG_CD = 'CAR' OR JO_CATG_CD = 'CMR' OR JO_CATG_CD = 'CVR' OR JO_CATG_CD = 'PUR' OR JO_CATG_CD = 'PVR', 2, -1 )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_JO_CATG_CD

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: //TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(AU_A_DT,'DD-MM-YYYY') || AU_A_TM, 'DD-MM-YYYYHH24.MI.SS') IIF(ISNULL(AU_A_DT) OR ISNULL(AU_A_TM), NULL, TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(AU_A_DT,'DD-MM-YYYY') || AU_A_TM, 'DD-MM-YYYYHH24.MI.SS'))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_AU_A_DT_TM

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: AC_CO_NR || AC_INTRL_ID || to_char(SN_CYC_BGN_DT,'YYYYMMDD') || to_char(GU_EFF_DT,'YYYYMMDD') || JO_PSTG_SEQ_NR || JO_INTRL_SEQ_NR || SUBSTR(TO_CHAR(TC_UPDT_TS,'YYYY-MM-DD-HH24.MI.SS.US'),-4,4)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_ID_MOV

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: DECODE(TRUE, FL_MOTO = 'S' AND (CO_TP_ECOM_SICU != '05' OR CO_TP_ECOM_SICU != '06'), 3, FL_MOTO = 'S' AND (CO_TP_ECOM_SICU = '05' OR CO_TP_ECOM_SICU = '06'), 4, FL_INTERNET = 'S' AND (CO_TP_ECOM_SICU != '05' OR CO_TP_ECOM_SICU != '06'), 1, FL_INTERNET = 'S' AND (CO_TP_ECOM_SICU = '05' OR CO_TP_ECOM_SICU = '06'), 2, FL_CLESS = 'S' AND JO_PSTD_AM >= 25, 5, FL_CLESS = 'S' AND JO_PSTD_AM < 25, 6, FL_CHIP = 'S', 7, FL_CHIP != 'S', 8, -1 )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_FL_MOTO

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: DECODE(TRUE, PRESENTMENT_IN='1','First Presentment', PRESENTMENT_IN='2','Second Presentment', PRESENTMENT_IN )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_PRESENTMENT_IN
